main event: An automobile-like object was observed dropping to an estimated 200-300 feet above the ground and moving at a high rate of speed in Silver Springs, Maryland.
interesting points: The object was described as cigar-shaped, approximately 40-50 feet in length, and having a metallic or dull gray color,The object had no visible wings or propulsion system,The sighting lasted for about 5-10 minutes,The object appeared to tilt slightly and was illuminated,No photographs or physical evidence were obtained.
witness description: The witness reported observing the object visually.
